      <title><![CDATA[MonoDB CRUD 操作]]></title>
      <url>http://dreamerking.github.io/king/2016/01/16/MonoDB-base-operate/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="创建文档并插入文档"><a href="#创建文档并插入文档" class="headerlink" title="创建文档并插入文档"></a>创建文档并插入文档</h1><p>插入文档使用 <code>insert(document)</code>函数，如果要批量插入，可以使用<code>batchInser(Array)</code>函数。<br>单个插入<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">post = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"title"</span> : <span class="string">"MonogoDB的基本操作"</span>,</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"content"</span> ：<span class="string">"这里详细介绍了一些基本操作。"</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">"date"</span> : new Date()</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">db.blog.inser(post)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>插入成功后会返回:<code>WriteResult({ &quot;nInserted&quot; : 1 })</code> 其中nInserted表示当前操作插入文档的数量。<br>以文档数组形式批量插入<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">db.test.insert([ </span><br><span class="line">    &#123; <span class="string">"name"</span>:<span class="string">"李平"</span>, <span class="string">"age"</span>:26&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">    &#123; <span class="string">"name"</span>:<span class="string">"吴晓菲"</span>, <span class="string">"age"</span>:18&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    ])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>插入成功后返回：<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">BulkWriteResult(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"writeErrors"</span> : [ ],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"writeConcernErrors"</span> : [ ],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"nInserted"</span> : 2,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"nUpserted"</span> : 0,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"nMatched"</span> : 0,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"nModified"</span> : 0,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"nRemoved"</span> : 0,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">"upserted"</span> : [ ]</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">``` </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#  更新文档    </span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">更新文档使用`update()`方法。要更新文档中某个字段的值，可以使用如`<span class="variable">$set</span>`这类的修改器。</span><br><span class="line">```sh</span><br><span class="line">    db.test.update(</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;<span class="string">"name"</span>:<span class="string">"李平"</span>&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable">$set</span>:&#123;age:20&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable">$currentDate</span>:&#123;lastModified:<span class="literal">true</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        )</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>更新成功返回:<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">WriteResult(&#123; <span class="string">"nMatched"</span> : 1, <span class="string">"nUpserted"</span> : 0, <span class="string">"nModified"</span> : 1 &#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p>]]></content>
    </entry>
    
    <entry>
      <title><![CDATA[let -- Shell]]></title>
      <url>http://dreamerking.github.io/king/2016/01/13/let/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="功能"><a href="#功能" class="headerlink" title="功能"></a>功能</h3><p>Shell中执行表达式运算的工具，可以执行常见的运算，还可以执行方幂运算<code>**</code>。<br><strong>注意</strong>:在let可做用的范围内不需要加<code>$</code>来表示变量，其次let可以用来解析字符串并执行运算。<br>另外let执行计算时，如果计算结果为非0时返回状态值为0;否则返回状态值为1。<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">let</span> a=23 b=12 c=a+b  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span>  <span class="variable">$a</span>  <span class="variable">$b</span>  <span class="variable">$c</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>执行结果：23 12 35</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">b=5  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">let</span> <span class="string">"t = ((a = 5 + 3, b = b - 1, c = 15 - 4))"</span>  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span>  <span class="variable">$t</span>  <span class="variable">$a</span>  <span class="variable">$b</span>  <span class="variable">$c</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>执行结果：11 8 4 11</p><h3 id="比较区别-加深理解"><a href="#比较区别-加深理解" class="headerlink" title="比较区别,加深理解"></a>比较区别,加深理解</h3><p>不使用let直接执行<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">t=32  </span><br><span class="line">t=<span class="variable">$t</span>+4  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$t</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>执行结果:32+4<br>使用let执行<br></p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">t=32   </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">let</span> t=<span class="variable">$t</span>+4  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> <span class="variable">$t</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p></p><p>执行结果:36<br><strong>结论：</strong>在Shell中，变量是无类型的。如果变量的值都是数字，则视为数值；如果含有字符，则视为字符串。</p>]]></content>
